                        </p>
                        <p className="text-xs text-gray-400">
                            Leave empty to revert to the default demo key (Rate limited).
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <label className="block text-xs font-bold text-gray-700 mb-1 uppercase tracking-wider">API Key</label>
